metadata.description: CB Sai M&M Looks are 7,302 unique 3D interactive model figures with traits inspired by CODEBOY Sai’s mixtape titled ‘Meetings & Makeups’. Each token holder unlocks access to 'Meetings & Makeups' via CODEBOY Sai’s token gated music player. Token holders play a role in managing CODEBOY Sai’s music career by holding a position within 'CODE LIFE Records DAO', a decentralized music label with a M2E (manage to earn) ecosystem.
metadata.name: Code Boy SAI Looks #0001
